Ororei le Enkai oimua Enkerai enye


1  Eirorie apa Enkai iloo papa too nkoitoi kumok o too mpukunot kumok too loibonok le Enkai; 
2  kake ore te kuna olong'i naabayie neirorie iyiook to Inoti otegelua ninye metaa olajung'oni loo ntokitin pooki, olaa te ninye eitayioki enkop. 
3  Ninye oitodolu enatiu enkisisa e Enkai naa ninye otaa olmishire le naikununo Enkai, naa ninye oibung'ita shumata o enkop to rorei le ngolon enye. Ore apa pee eidip aitobira enkipooto oo ng'ok, neton te tatene e Nkitoo te shumata.

Enkitoo Enkerai Enkai


4  Eidipa ninye aisula ilmalaika amu ore enkarna nanoto naa ninye nalusoo te nenye. 
5   Amu kalo malaika etiaaka Enkai ae kata nchere, “Ira iyie Oinoti lai latoiwuo te le kekun?” Aashu sii, “Kaaku nanu menye lenye, neaku ninye Oinoti lai?” 
6   O sii, pee eyau olkikau lenye enkop nejo, “Inchoo eserem ninye ilmalaika pooki le Enkai.” 
7   Ore ti alo ilmalaika nejo ninye, “Oloitaa ilmalaika lenyena isiwuon, neitaa isinkan lenyena ilng'ejepa le nkima.” 
8   Kake etejo ti alo Oinoti lenye, “Ore olorika lino, iyie Enkai naa oloo ntarasi o ntarasi orinka le supatisho ilo rinka le nkitoria ino. 
9  Itonyorra iyie esupatisho nimbayu engogong'i ore enkaraki ina nikitubukoko Enkai ino eilata aput, nikiela te ilata e ng'ida nalang ene sirit ino.” 
10   Ore sii, “Iyie, Olaitoriani, oitobira enkop te nkiterunoto, ore shumata naa esiaai oo nkaik inono. 
11  Keishari ninche, kake ibik ake iyie, kemusanu ninche, kake ibik ake iyie, kemusanu ninche anaa enkila, 
12  naa iyie oyooki apiyai ninche anaa enkila neibelekenya ninche. Kake itiu iyie anaa apake, nemeishunye ilarin linono ntarasi.”


13   Kake kalo malaika etiaaka ae kata, “Totona te nkaina ai e tatene, o metaba anaa naitaa ilmang'ati linono olorika loo nkejek inono?” 
14  Aime nkiyang'eta aisiaayiak ake ninche pooki naairriwayioki meisiaaisho, te nkaraki lelo ootum enjeunoto?

